dct_description_sm: Morocco. Qism al-Khara'itiyah. Morocco. Mudiriyat al-Muhafazah al-'Aqariyah wa-al-Ashghal al-Tubughrafiyah. France.Institut geographique national. Relief shown by 5 meter contour interval and spot heights. Includes location map and index to points of interest. With a transliteration table. Copyright: "Direction de la Conservation Fonciere et des Travaux Topographiques, Rabat, 1977." Copyright: "Institut Geographique National, Paris, 1977.".
